   <category name='food'>

      <section name='fur'>

         <para number='1' comment='Buy food Breakfast in Fur 1509'>
         A waitdroid, which is also covered in fur to match the decor, places a large tray on the table in front of you. On the tray are fourteen small dishes, each containing a few forkfuls of food. This is the ultimate in taster menus! You tuck in with relish, enjoying the contrasts of flavors and textures between all the different foodstuffs. Faster than you expected, it has all gone, and you are left with the memory of the melange of tastes.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Not enuff groats'>
         A waitdroid, which is also covered in fur to match the decor, points out that you don't have any money.
         </para>

